      <title>英国严厉打击剥削移民工人的企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/uk-launches-crackdown-on-firms-exploiting-migrant-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府宣布严厉打击剥削移民工人的不法雇主，禁止违法者再雇用任何海外员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/uk-launches-crackdown-on-firms-exploiting-migrant-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
